<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 02:22:33 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国会领导人宣布就支出水平达成协议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/congressional-leaders-announce-an-agreement-on-spending-levels-a-key-step-to-averting-shutdown/articleshow/106620361.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106620361.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;国会领导人已就总体支出水平达成协议，以避免政府部分关闭。该协议遵守国防和国内计划的支出上限，但向众议院共和党人做出让步。众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示，该协议确保额外削减 160 亿美元的开支。这比参议院考虑的金额少了 300 亿美元。该协议还加快了已经商定的国税局削减计划，并取消了 60 亿美元的新冠疫情救助资金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 00:25:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/congressional-leaders-announce-an-agreement-on-spending-levels-a-key-step-to-averting-shutdown/articleshow/106620361.cms</guid></item><item><title>国防部长对白宫住院情况一无所知</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/defence-secretary-keeps-white-house-in-dark-about-hospitalisation/articleshow/106620261.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106620261.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;五角大楼违反协议，花了三天半的时间才向白宫通报国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀住院的情况。奥斯汀因手术并发症住院治疗，直到周四才向高级国防官员透露。延迟的通知让政府官员感到困惑，奥斯汀发表了道歉，并为缺乏披露承担责任。拜登总统对奥斯汀表示充满信心，奥斯汀此后已恢复履职。该事件引发了人们对沟通中断和需要承担后果的担忧。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:59:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/defence-secretary-keeps-white-house-in-dark-about-hospitalisation/articleshow/106620261.cms</guid></item><item><title>反对派发起民意调查导致巴基斯坦互联网中断</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-internet-disrupted-as-opposition-launches-poll-campaign/articleshow/106620257.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106620257.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周日晚上，巴基斯坦各地的互联网和社交媒体服务受到严重干扰，被监禁的前总理伊姆兰·汗的政党准备在选举前发起大规模的在线竞选活动。汗和他的巴基斯坦正义运动党 (PTI) 的大多数高级领导人已被拒绝作为 2 月 8 日投票的候选人，他们称这是军方领导的机构为阻止他们参与而发起的一场运动。 PTI 计划在周日晚上举办一场大规模的全国和全球电视马拉松，以发布其宣言并筹集竞选资金，但互联网从傍晚开始就出现中断。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:57:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-internet-disrupted-as-opposition-launches-poll-campaign/articleshow/106620257.cms</guid></item><item><title>在国会大厦骚乱周年纪念日，唐纳德·特朗普淡化围攻，称被监禁的骚乱者为“人质”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/on-capitol-riot-anniversary-donald-trump-downplays-siege-calls-jailed-rioters-hostages/articleshow/106620235.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106620235.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普发起爱荷华州竞选活动，誓言要第三次获胜。他嘲笑拜登的经济衰退和边境混乱，指责他为俄罗斯入侵乌克兰负责。特朗普警告称，如果拜登连任，将爆发第三次世界大战，称这是拯救美国的最后机会。特朗普的竞争对手黑利和德桑蒂斯在爱荷华州竞选。特朗普批评黑莉对内战的评论，暗示内战本来可以通过谈判解决。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:48:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/on-capitol-riot-anniversary-donald-trump-downplays-siege-calls-jailed-rioters-hostages/articleshow/106620235.cms</guid></item><item><title>一声轰鸣，一声嗖嗖，一声闪烁：“我开始给我所爱的人发短信”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/a-boom-a-whoosh-a-flicker-i-started-to-text-my-loved-ones/articleshow/106620156.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106620156.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:25:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/a-boom-a-whoosh-a-flicker-i-started-to-text-my-loved-ones/articleshow/106620156.cms</guid></item><item><title>不丹明天投票，经济冲突影响“国民幸福”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bhutan-votes-tomorrow-as-economic-strife-hits-national-happiness/articleshow/106620214.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106620214.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;不丹在经济挑战以及对长期青年失业和人才流失的担忧之际举行大选。该国将“国民幸福总值”置于经济增长之上的政策受到质疑。选举中的两党都致力于人民的福祉。年轻一代的挣扎，包括移居国外和空荡荡的村庄，是关键问题。疫情扰乱了旅游业，各方计划加大对水电和其他行业的投资。由于战略边境地区的关系，此次选举受到中国和印度的密切关注。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bhutan-votes-tomorrow-as-economic-strife-hits-national-happiness/articleshow/106620214.cms</guid></item><item><title>贾斯汀·特鲁多的飞机自G20印度访问以来第二次发生故障</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/justin-trudeaus-jet-breaks-down-for-2nd-time-since-g20-india-visit/articleshow/106620202.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106620202.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 23:39:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/justin-trudeaus-jet-breaks-down-for-2nd-time-since-g20-india-visit/articleshow/106620202.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国谢赫·哈西娜赢得连任：民意调查小组</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladeshs-sheikh-hasina-wins-re-election-election-commission/articleshow/106617295.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106617295.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;官员们称，孟加拉国总理谢赫·哈西娜周日赢得连任，第五次连任，此前她将其称为“恐怖组织”的反对党领导了抵制活动。哈西娜执政的人民联盟“赢得了超过 50% 的席位”。计票工作正在进行中，选举委员会发言人告诉法新社。在她主持下，这个曾经饱受贫困困扰的国家实现了惊人的经济增长，但她的政府却被指控猖獗的侵犯人权行为和残酷镇压反对派。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 17:38:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladeshs-sheikh-hasina-wins-re-election-election-commission/articleshow/106617295.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国选举委员会应用程序因乌克兰和德国网络攻击而变慢：官方</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bangladesh-election-commission-app-slowed-down-after-cyber-attack-from-ukraine-germany-official/articleshow/106616917.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106616917.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 16:53:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/bangladesh-election-commission-app-slowed-down-after-cyber-attack-from-ukraine-germany-official/articleshow/106616917.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国首相里希·苏纳克承诺对影响许多英属印度人的邮局丑闻采取行动</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-pm-rishi-sunak-pledges-action-over-post-office-scandal-impacting-many-british-indians/articleshow/106616456.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106616456.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国首相里希·苏纳克正在审查涉及副邮政局长被错误指控欺诈的会计丑闻的赔偿程序。司法部长正在寻求加快推翻错误定罪和提供赔偿的进程。被撤销定罪的 39 名副邮政局长包括 Seema Biswas 和 Vijay Parekh。受害者仍在等待合法的无罪和赔偿，这被称为英国历史上最大的误判之一。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/british-pm-rishi-sunak-pledges-action-over-post-office-scandal-impacting-many-british-indians/articleshow/106616456.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯访问中东，加沙战争进入第四个月</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-war-rages-into-fourth-month-as-blinken-tours-middle-east/articleshow/106616409.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106616409.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;随着以色列军队继续袭击巴勒斯坦领土，加沙战争进入第四个月。以色列的轰炸已造成至少 113 人死亡，其中包括两名为半岛电视台工作的记者。以色列军队报告在加沙中部杀死了更多“恐怖分子”，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡誓言将继续下去，直到取得彻底胜利。以色列和真主党之间也爆发了暴力冲突，双方交火。美国高级外交官安东尼·布林肯访问中东以防止局势进一步升级，会见约旦国王阿卜杜拉二世并讨论加沙停火。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 15:53:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-war-rages-into-fourth-month-as-blinken-tours-middle-east/articleshow/106616409.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京誓言支持“手握武器”的士兵，但没有呼吁乌克兰在东正教圣诞节停火</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-president-putin-vows-support-to-soldiers-with-arms-in-hands-omits-call-for-ukraine-ceasefire-on-orthodox-christmas/articleshow/106614568.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106614568.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京表示坚定不移地致力于支持士兵在东正教圣诞节捍卫俄罗斯的利益。他呼吁为保卫国家的人们提供更多援助。普京与在乌克兰冲突中失去亲人的家庭一起参加了一场亲密的午夜仪式。与前一年相反，没有人呼吁停火。俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的冲突始于 2022 年 2 月，已导致数千人伤亡、数百万人流离失所。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 12:38:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-president-putin-vows-support-to-soldiers-with-arms-in-hands-omits-call-for-ukraine-ceasefire-on-orthodox-christmas/articleshow/106614568.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国报纸网站因国家投票而被封锁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-newspaper-site-blocked-as-country-votes/articleshow/106614560.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106614560.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;孟加拉国批评报纸《马纳布日报》报道称，其网站在大选期间被封锁，大选遭到反对党的抵制。尽管网站被封锁，但街头仍然可以买到该报纸的印刷版。总理谢赫·哈西娜预计将赢得第五个任期，但她的政府面临侵犯人权和镇压反对派的指控。无国界记者组织就孟加拉国政府对信息的控制发出警告。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 12:35:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/bangladesh-newspaper-site-blocked-as-country-votes/articleshow/106614560.cms</guid></item><item><title>迷幻蘑菇在 SpaceX 活动中胡言乱语：埃隆·马斯克因涉嫌吸毒而受到审查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/psychedelic-mushrooms-rambling-at-spacex-event-elon-musk-under-scrutiny-over-alleged-drug-use/articleshow/106614401.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106614401.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，埃隆·马斯克使用迷幻药物，包括 LSD、氯胺酮和迷幻蘑菇，引起了特斯拉和 SpaceX 董事会成员的担忧。马斯克偶尔的爆发和喜怒无常的行为在沃尔特·艾萨克森的传记中被描述为“恶魔模式”，这归因于他紧张的工作日程和很少的睡眠。他的连贯性也受到质疑，高管们声称他在 SpaceX 的一次活动中口齿不清、胡言乱语。马斯克在 Joe Rogan Show 上吸食大麻，以及他在私人聚会上吸毒的指控，导致 NASA 提出担忧，并对 SpaceX 人员进行了随机药物测试。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 12:31:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/psychedelic-mushrooms-rambling-at-spacex-event-elon-musk-under-scrutiny-over-alleged-drug-use/articleshow/106614401.cms</guid></item><item><title>两名记者在周日以色列袭击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/two-journalists-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-sunday/articleshow/106614385.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106614385.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列空袭导致车内两名记者穆斯塔法·图里亚 (Mustafa Thuria) 和哈姆扎·瓦尔·达杜 (Hamza Wael Dahdouh) 丧生。穆斯塔法是法新社的视频特约记者，哈姆扎是半岛电视台的记者。哈姆扎的父亲瓦尔·达赫杜 (Wael al-Dahdouh) 是半岛电视台加沙分社社长，此前在以色列袭击中受伤。迄今为止，已有77名记者和媒体工作者在以色列和哈马斯之间的战争中丧生，其中大多数是巴勒斯坦人。哈马斯政府媒体办公室谴责以色列军队的行为，法新社已要求以色列军方发表评论。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 12:27:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/two-journalists-killed-in-israeli-strike-on-sunday/articleshow/106614385.cms</guid></item><item><title>梅根·马克尔的母亲在“艰难时期”介入支持她和哈里王子</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meghan-markles-mother-steps-in-to-support-her-and-prince-harry-during-tough-times/articleshow/106613932.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106613932.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;梅根·马克尔的母亲多莉亚·拉格兰 (Doria Ragland) 已搬进哈里王子和梅根的蒙特西托宅邸内的宾馆。这位 67 岁的瑜伽老师在充满挑战的一年里一直为这对夫妇提供持续的支持。当梅根和哈利在好莱坞的事业遭遇挫折时，多莉亚的出现尤其有帮助。她已成为家庭中的母亲角色，照顾孙子，并为哈利提供他需要的独处时间。这种密切的联系分散了人们与英国家庭持续紧张的关系。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 11:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/meghan-markles-mother-steps-in-to-support-her-and-prince-harry-during-tough-times/articleshow/106613932.cms</guid></item><item><title>孟加拉国罗辛亚难民营发生火灾，烧毁了 1000 多个避难所</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/a-fire-in-a-rohingya-refugee-camp-in-bangladesh-guts-more-than-1000-shelters/articleshow/106613288.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106613288.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;孟加拉国科克斯巴扎尔的库图帕隆难民营发生火灾，摧毁了 1000 多个避难所，导致数千名罗兴亚难民无家可归。由于强风，火势迅速蔓延，但最终被消防志愿者控制住。没有人员伤亡报告。据信，起火原因是泥炉，这是难民营中常见的火源。这一事件加剧了因迫害和歧视而逃离缅甸的罗兴亚难民所面临的持续挑战。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 11:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/a-fire-in-a-rohingya-refugee-camp-in-bangladesh-guts-more-than-1000-shelters/articleshow/106613288.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国称朝鲜连续第三天在其海域边界附近发射炮弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-says-north-korea-has-fired-artillery-near-their-sea-boundary-for-a-third-straight-day/articleshow/106612789.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106612789.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;韩国军方强烈敦促朝鲜停止挑衅行为，朝鲜连续第三天在海上边界附近发射炮弹。朝鲜颇具影响力的妹妹金与正嘲笑韩国探测武器发射的能力，并否认向海中发射炮弹的说法。韩国军方将她的声明斥为“低级心理战”，并警告将对任何挑衅行为做出严厉回应。朝韩两国都建立了海上缓冲区。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 10:45:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-says-north-korea-has-fired-artillery-near-their-sea-boundary-for-a-third-straight-day/articleshow/106612789.cms</guid></item><item><title>反印度神职人员阿拉马·马苏德·乌斯马尼在伊斯兰堡被暗杀</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/anti-india-cleric-allama-masood-ur-rehman-usmani-assassinated-in-islamabad/articleshow/106611442.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106611442.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;著名反印度神职人员阿拉马·马苏杜尔·拉赫曼·乌斯马尼 (Allama Masoodur Rehman Usmani) 光天化日之下在巴基斯坦伊斯兰堡郊区被暗杀。两名身份不明的枪手开枪打死乌斯马尼，打伤他的司机，然后逃离现场。由于此次袭击在巴基斯坦这一地区很少发生，因此引起了人们的关注。警方已将乌斯马尼的尸体和受伤司机转移至巴基斯坦医学科学研究所，以采取进一步行动。截至目前，尚无组织声称对这起暗杀事件负责。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 08:59:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/anti-india-cleric-allama-masood-ur-rehman-usmani-assassinated-in-islamabad/articleshow/106611442.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜连续第三天发射炮弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/tensions-surge-as-north-korea-fires-artillery-for-third-consecutive-day-kims-sister-mocks-south-korea-issues-stern-warning/articleshow/106612719.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106612719.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜在与韩国有争议的海域边界附近发射炮弹，加剧了紧张局势。韩国军方敦促朝鲜停止挑衅行为。朝鲜领导人的妹妹金与正驳斥了韩国的指控并嘲笑他们的侦查能力。韩国将她的声明描述为“低级心理战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jan 2024 10:20:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/tensions-surge-as-north-korea-fires-artillery-for-third-consecutive-day-kims-sister-mocks-south-korea-issues-stern-warning/articleshow/106612719.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>